# Edge — WC2026 Betting Engine
# Client-side (VITE_) environment variables.
# These names document which third-party APIs the app uses. The actual key
# VALUES live server-side as Lovable Cloud secrets (no VITE_ prefix) and are
# used only by the api-proxy server function, so they never ship to the browser.

# api-sports.io (API-Football) — server secret: APIFOOTBALL_KEY
# Stats, H2H, injuries, predictions, Stake odds, referee.
VITE_APIFOOTBALL_KEY=

# thestatsapi.com (TheStatsAPI) — server secret: STATSAPI_KEY
# Confirmed lineups + Pinnacle odds / line movement.
# Sign up at https://thestatsapi.com for an API key (Bearer auth).
VITE_STATSAPI_KEY=

# NOTE: The Anthropic key is intentionally NOT here. It lives server-side as the
# ANTHROPIC_KEY secret and is only used by the analyse-match server function.
